{
  "texts": [
    "For fitting s(t), we employ thin plate regression splines.",
    "Users not tweeting in either of the two languages of the respective language pair, need to be discarded by definition.",
    "Hence, for UA over RU our estimation sample consists of of x = 194,178 observations, with t = 143 weeks and u = 10,531 users.",
    "For UA over EN: x = 146,984, t = 143, u = 9,133.",
    "For RU over EN: x = 170,853, t = 143, u = 10777."
  ]
}